Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Dao in the Province of Antique to Tobias Fornier
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 10
An Act Changing the Name of the Municipality of Dao in the Province of Antique to Tobias Fornier
Section 1. The name of the Municipality of Dao in the Province of Antique is hereby changed to Tobias Fornier.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: December 6, 1978
